values: My name is Alison Collina, but you can call me Allie. I am a bitch, and proud of it. I've had so many people calling me a bitch and thinking it hurts me, when really, it makes me feel great inside! I'm not always a bitch though, I can be nice. I'm a normal person. I keep secrets. I let secrets slip sometimes. I love. I lust. I hate. I like. I shop. I goof around. Sue me. I play sports. I play instruments. I sing. I dance. I act. Wanna know more? Hit me up on AIM;; YouSmellLikeDirt
